  "title": "Sales Supervisor (North-East Area)",
  "description": "<p>📍<strong> Serangoon/ Punggol </strong><br />⏰ Min. 8-10 hrs shift per day <em><strong>(Schedule will be based on roster; No fix morning shift)</strong></em><br />📅 6-days work week<br />💰 Up to $3,800/month <br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u><br />• Supervise daily shop operations, including opening and closing duties.<br />• Lead, motivate and coach staffs to achieve sales targets.<br />• Deliver excellent customer service and handle customers' feedback professionally.<br />• Ensure proper product display, freshness and visual merchandising standards.<br />• Monitor stock levels, replenishment and control wastage. <br />• Prepare staffs' duty rosters and manage manpower effectively.<br />• Ensure compliance with food hygiene, safety and company's SOPs.<br />• Assist in sales reporting and implementation of promotions. <br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u><br />• <strong>Singaporeans Only</strong><br />• Min. 2-3 years of supervisory experience in retail/ F&B. <br />• Strong leadership and communication skills. <br />• Customer-oriented with a positive attitude.<br />• Able to work shifts, weekends and public holidays.<br />• Knowledge of food hygiene and safety standards is an advantage. <br /></p><p><u><strong>Staffs' Benefits:</strong></u><br />• Annual & Medical leaves entitlement <br />• Medical claims <br />• AWS/ VB<br />• Annual salary increment <em><strong>(based on individuals' work performance)</strong></em><br />• Attendance, weekend & public holiday allowances <br />• OT payable <br /></p><p>📱 Interested applicants, can <strong>WhatsApp @ 84944246</strong> OR <strong>Tele: @fourleaveshr</strong></p>",
